<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1324,1427,1893]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Remarks. — The female of 
<taxonomicName box="[637,850,1428,1453]" class="Malacostraca" family="Phoxocephalidae" genus="Harpinia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="truncata">
